      "source": [
        "# 3D Voxel Visualization from PDB"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 1. Install Dependencies (Optional)\n",
        "Make sure you have installed the following Python packages:\n",
        "```bash\n",
        "pip install biopython numpy pandas matplotlib scikit-image torch torchvision tqdm scipy\n",
